==產業報告==
國際音樂峰會2014年商業報告中估計電子舞曲產業市場值為62億美元一年<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.internationalmusicsummit.com/img/stand_alone_files/file/original/ims-business-report-2014-vfinal-12.pdf|title=IMS Business Report 2014|year=2014|accessdate=2016-09-18|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922195959/https://www.internationalmusicsummit.com/img/stand_alone_files/file/original/ims-business-report-2014-vfinal-12.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

